Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pyndexter
Version: 0.2
Summary: An abstraction layer for full-text indexing engines.
Home-page: http://swapoff.org/pyndexter
Author: Alec Thomas
Author-email: alec@swapoff.org
License: BSD
Download-URL: http://swapoff.org/pyndexter
Description: Pyndexter (pronounced 'poindexter') is an abstraction layer for full-text indexing engines. It presents a uniform query syntax to the user, includes a basic but functional pure-Python indexer, and has adapters for Hype, Hyperestraier, Lucene, Lupy, Pyndex, Swish-e and Xapian.
Platform: any
